# SHA-256 hashes for whisper.cpp models we ship or download.
#
# Format: one entry per line, `<sha256>  <filename>` (two-space separator,
# matching `shasum -a 256` output). Comments start with `#`.
#
# Used by `scripts/fetch-model.sh` to verify the downloaded artifact
# before placing it in `src-tauri/resources/models/`. A missing entry
# fails the fetch — populate this file when adding a new model.
#
# Source: hashes of the canonical `ggml-*.bin` and `*-encoder.mlmodelc.zip`
# artifacts published by ggerganov at
# https://huggingface.co/ggerganov/whisper.cpp.
c6138d6d58ecc8322097e0f987c32f1be8bb0a18532a3f88f734d1bbf9c41e5d  ggml-small.en.bin
b2ef1c506378b825b4b4341979a93e1656b5d6c129f17114cfb8fb78aabc2f89  ggml-small.en-encoder.mlmodelc.zip
